 Append  (cost=0.54..3479.55 rows=223770 width=20) (actual rows=223793.00 loops=1)
   ->  Custom Scan (ColumnarScan) on _hyper_3_8_chunk  (cost=0.54..806.31 rows=74531 width=20) (actual rows=74537.00 loops=1)
         ->  Seq Scan on _hyper_3_8_chunk_compressed  (cost=0.00..61.00 rows=1500 width=88) (actual rows=1500.00 loops=1)
